title: Wildlife Management Area Boundary (polygon), Arkansas
name: Wildlife Management Area Boundary (polygon), Arkansas
description: Arkansas Game &amp; Fish Commission Wildlife Management Areas. WMA shapefiles with revision dates prior to 2002  were digitized into AutoCad version 13 &amp; above; from deed and plat book information using hard copy topo maps and State Plane coordinates.  Conversion to UTM Nad 27  ESRI shapefiles was completed in ArcView 3x and to UTM Nad 83 projection in ArcMap version 8x. Areas with a revision date of 2002 or later have been revised for ArcMap 8x or higher using UTM Nad 83 projection.  Acreage information is based on shapefile area calculations.
